data.description: Welcome to 1057 Karen Dr, a beautifully renovated home located in the desirable Cambridge Subdivision of Joliet.  Built in 1989, this charming residence offers a perfect blend of classic design and modern updates. This split level home has plenty of space including 3 bedrooms with new flooring and paint and 2 recently renovated bathrooms.  Some of the updates to the home include new flooring, new cabinets and counter tops, and newer appliances to mention a few.  Newer furnace/humidifier (2018), new AC (2021), and new Samsung stainless steel convection oven (2020).  The home also features a spacious backyard perfect for entertaining guests. This home has been extremely well kept so don't miss your chance to make 1057 Karen Dr your new home.
